\r\\n            font-size: 1.1em;\\r\\n            color: #dcdcdc;\\r\\n            line-height: 1.6em;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n\\r\\n        .section-image {\\r\\n            margin-top: 20px;\\r\\n            display: flex;\\r\\n            justify-content: center;\\r\\n            align-items: center;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .section-image img {\\r\\n            max-width: 80%;\\r\\n            border-radius: 10px;\\r\\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\\r\\n            transition: transform 0.3s;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .section-image img:hover {\\r\\n            transform: scale(1.1);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n\\r\\n        \\/* Footer *\\/\\r\\n        footer {\\r\\n            background: #004d40;\\r\\n            padding: 20px;\\r\\n            text-align: center;\\r\\n            color: #ffffff;\\r\\n            font-size: 0.9em;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    <\\/style>\\r\\n<\\/head>\\r\\n<body>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <!-- Header -->\\r\\n    <header>\\r\\n        <h1>El Origen de las Criptomonedas<\\/h1>\\r\\n        <p>Descubre c\\u00f3mo nacieron y cambiaron el mundo financiero<\\/p>\\r\\n    <\\/header>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <!-- Section 1 -->\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-content\\\">\\r\\n            <h2>Contexto Hist\\u00f3rico<\\/h2>\\r\\n            <p>\\r\\n                En 2008, tras la crisis financiera, surgi\\u00f3 una nueva idea: un sistema financiero sin bancos ni intermediarios. As\\u00ed naci\\u00f3 Bitcoin, presentado en un documento llamado \\\"Bitcoin: A Peer-to-Peer Electronic Cash System\\\".\\r\\n            <\\/p>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-image\\\">\\r\\n            <img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/proyectofinaljoomla\\/images\\/bankss.jpeg\\\" alt=\\\"Crisis financiera 2008\\\">\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <!-- Section 2 -->\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-content\\\">\\r\\n            <h2>El C\\u00f3digo Fundacional<\\/h2>\\r\\n            <p>\\r\\n                Bitcoin se bas\\u00f3 en un c\\u00f3digo descentralizado que usa blockchain, garantizando transacciones seguras. El suministro total est\\u00e1 limitado a 21 millones de monedas, evitando la inflaci\\u00f3n.\\r\\n            <\\/p>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-image\\\">\\r\\n            <img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/proyectofinaljoomla\\/images\\/cashbtc.jpeg\\\" alt=\\\"C\\u00f3digo de Bitcoin\\\">\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <!-- Section 3 -->\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-content\\\">\\r\\n            <h2>Or\\u00edgenes T\\u00e9cnicos<\\/h2>\\r\\n            <p>\\r\\n                Bitcoin tom\\u00f3 ideas de proyectos previos como Hashcash y b-money. Su \\u00e9xito radica en la combinaci\\u00f3n de estas ideas con un sistema de incentivos para los mineros.\\r\\n            <\\/p>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-image\\\">\\r\\n            <img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/proyectofinaljoomla\\/images\\/trade.jpeg\\\" alt=\\\"Primeros conceptos de criptomonedas\\\">\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <!-- Section 4 -->\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-content\\\">\\r\\n            <h2>El Inicio de una Revoluci\\u00f3n<\\/h2>\\r\\n            <p>\\r\\n                Bitcoin comenz\\u00f3 como una idea peque\\u00f1a, pero pronto revolucion\\u00f3 el concepto de dinero digital. Hoy, las criptomonedas est\\u00e1n cambiando el sistema financiero global.\\r\\n            <\\/p>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-image\\\">\\r\\n            <img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/proyectofinaljoomla\\/images\\/defi.jpeg\\\" alt=\\\"Revoluci\\u00f3n de las criptomonedas\\\">\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <!-- Footer -->\\r\\n    <footer>\\r\\n        <p>&