;\\r\\n            color: #dcdcdc;\\r\\n            line-height: 1.6em;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n\\r\\n        .section-image {\\r\\n            flex: 1 1 50%;\\r\\n            display: flex;\\r\\n            justify-content: center;\\r\\n            align-items: center;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .section-image img {\\r\\n            max-width: 90%;\\r\\n            border-radius: 10px;\\r\\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\\r\\n            transition: transform 0.3s;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .section-image img:hover {\\r\\n            transform: scale(1.1);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n\\r\\n        \\/* Interactive Module *\\/\\r\\n        .interactive-box {\\r\\n            background: #003366;\\r\\n            padding: 20px;\\r\\n            margin: 20px auto;\\r\\n            max-width: 600px;\\r\\n            border-radius: 10px;\\r\\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\\r\\n            text-align: center;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .interactive-box h3 {\\r\\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\\r\\n            color: #00e676;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .interactive-box select {\\r\\n            width: 100%;\\r\\n            padding: 10px;\\r\\n            margin-top: 10px;\\r\\n            border: none;\\r\\n            border-radius: 5px;\\r\\n            background: #004d40;\\r\\n            color: #ffffff;\\r\\n            font-family: \'Arial\', sans-serif;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .interactive-box button {\\r\\n            margin-top: 15px;\\r\\n            padding: 10px 20px;\\r\\n            background-color: #00e676;\\r\\n            color: #0d0d0d;\\r\\n            border: none;\\r\\n            border-radius: 5px;\\r\\n            cursor: pointer;\\r\\n            font-size: 1em;\\r\\n            transition: background-color 0.3s;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .interactive-box button:hover {\\r\\n            background-color: #66ffa6;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n\\r\\n        \\/* Footer *\\/\\r\\n        footer {\\r\\n            background: #004d40;\\r\\n            padding: 20px;\\r\\n            text-align: center;\\r\\n            color: #ffffff;\\r\\n            font-size: 0.9em;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    <\\/style>\\r\\n<\\/head>\\r\\n<body>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <!-- Header -->\\r\\n    <header>\\r\\n        <h1>El Misterio de Satoshi Nakamoto<\\/h1>\\r\\n        <p>Descubre la enigma detr\\u00e1s del creador de Bitcoin<\\/p>\\r\\n    <\\/header>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <!-- Section 1 -->\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-content\\\">\\r\\n            <h2>\\u00bfQui\\u00e9n es Satoshi Nakamoto?<\\/h2>\\r\\n            <p>\\r\\n                Satoshi Nakamoto es el pseud\\u00f3nimo del creador de Bitcoin, la primera criptomoneda del mundo. A pesar de ser una figura clave en la revoluci\\u00f3n financiera digital, la identidad de Nakamoto sigue siendo un misterio. Desde la publicaci\\u00f3n del famoso \\\"whitepaper\\\" en 2008 hasta la creaci\\u00f3n de la red en 2009, Nakamoto ha permanecido en el anonimato, dejando a la comunidad cripto especulando sobre su verdadera identidad.\\r\\n            <\\/p>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-image\\\">\\r\\n            <img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/proyectofinaljoomla\\/images\\/satoshi.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Satoshi Nakamoto\\\">\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <!-- Section 2 -->\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-image\\\">\\r\\n            <img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/proyectofinaljoomla\\/images\\/bitcoin.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Bitcoin\\\">\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-content\\\">\\r\\n            <h2>El Enigma del Creador<\\/h2>\\r\\n            <p>\\r\\n                A lo largo de los a\\u00f1os, han surgido diversas teor\\u00edas sobre la identidad de Nakamoto. Algunos creen que es una persona, mientras que otros piensan que es un grupo de individuos. Algunos de los principales sospechosos incluyen a figuras como Hal Finney, Nick Szabo y Craig Wright, aunque ninguno de ellos ha podido demostrar ser el verdadero creador.\\r\\n            <\\/p>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <!-- Section 3 -->\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-content\\\">\\r\\n            <h2>\\u00bfPor qu\\u00e9 es importante el misterio?<\\/h2>\\r\\n            <p>\\r\\n                El anonimato de Satoshi Nakamoto ha generado debates sobre la centralizaci\\u00f3n y la descentralizaci\\u00f3n. Su desaparici\\u00f3n de la comunidad cripto despu\\u00e9s de 2011 ha dejado a Bitcoin en manos de la comunidad global, lo que refuerza la idea de que las criptomonedas pueden operar sin la necesidad de un l\\u00edder central. Este misterio tambi\\u00e9n a\\u00f1ade un aire de misticismo y fascinaci\\u00f3n alrededor de Bitcoin y su creador.\\r\\n            <\\/p>\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n        <div class=\\\"section-image\\\">\\r\\n            <img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/proyectofinaljoomla\\/images\\/blockchain.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Blockchain\\\">\\r\\n        <\\/div>\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n    <!-- Footer -->\\r\\n    <footer>\\r\\n        <p>&copy; 2025 CriptoMundo. Todos los derechos reservados.<\\/p>\\r\\n    <\\/footer>\\r\\n\\r\\n<\\/body>\\r\\n<\\/html>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":8,\"created\":\"2025-01-01 14:37:39\",\"created_by\":\"209\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2025-01-05 12:10:51\",\"modified_by\":208,\"checked_out\":208,\"checked_out_time\":\"2025-01-05 12:09:40\",\"publish_up\":\"2025-01-01 14:38:14\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\"