 line-height: 1.6em;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n\\r\\n        .section-image {\\r\\n            flex: 1 1 50%;\\r\\n            display: flex;\\r\\n            justify-content: center;\\r\\n            align-items: center;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .section-image img {\\r\\n            max-width: 90%;\\r\\n            border-radius: 10px;\\r\\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\\r\\n            transition: transform 0.3s;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .section-image img:hover {\\r\\n            transform: scale(1.1);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n\\r\\n        \\/* Interactive Module *\\/\\r\\n        .interactive-box {\\r\\n            background: #003366;\\r\\n            padding: 20px;\\r\\n            margin: 20px auto;\\r\\n            max-width: 600px;\\r\\n            border-radius: 10px;\\r\\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\\r\\n            text-align: center;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .interactive-box h3 {\\r\\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\\r\\n            color: #00e676;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .interactive-box select {\\r\\n            width: 100%;\\r\\n            padding: 10px;\\r\\n            margin-top: 10px;\\r\\n            border: none;\\r\\n            border-radius: 5px;\\r\\n            background: #004d40;\\r\\n            color: #ffffff;\\r\\n            font-family: \'Arial\', sans-serif;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .interactive-box button {\\r\\n            margin-top: 15px;\\r\\n            padding: 10px 20px;\\r\\n            background-color: #00e676;\\r\\n            color: #0d0d0d;\\r\\n            border: none;\\r\\n            border-radius: 5px;\\r\\n            cursor: pointer;\\r\\n            font-size: 1em;\\r\\n            transition: background-color 0.3s;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n        .interactive-box button:hover {\\r\\n            background-color: #66ffa6;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n\\r\\n        \\/* Footer *\\/\\r\\n        footer {\\r\\n            background: #004d40;\\r\\n            padding: 20px;\\r\\n            text-align: center;\\r\\n            color: #ffffff;\\r\\n            font-size: 0.9em;\\r\\n        }\\r\\n    <\\/style>\\r\\n<\\/head>\\r\\n<body>\\r\\n\\r\\n<!-- Header -->\\r\\n<header>\\r\\n    <h1>La Primera Estrella<\\/h1>\\r\\n    <p>Explora la historia detr\\u00e1s del nacimiento de Bitcoin y su impacto en el mundo financiero.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/header>\\r\\n\\r\\n<!-- Section 1: Introducci\\u00f3n -->\\r\\n<div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section-content\\\">\\r\\n        <h2>El Nacimiento de la Primera Estrella<\\/h2>\\r\\n        <p>\\r\\n            En 2009, el mundo de las finanzas cambi\\u00f3 para siempre con la creaci\\u00f3n de Bitcoin. La primera criptomoneda, nacida de una idea revolucionaria, \\r\\n            marc\\u00f3 el comienzo de una nueva era. Bitcoin no solo representa un cambio en la forma de manejar el dinero, sino tambi\\u00e9n un desaf\\u00edo directo a los sistemas financieros tradicionales.\\r\\n        <\\/p>\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section-image\\\">\\r\\n        <img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/proyectofinaljoomla\\/images\\/red.webp\\\" alt=\\\"Nacimiento de Bitcoin\\\">\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<!-- Section 2: Cr\\u00edticas y Resistencia -->\\r\\n<div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section-image\\\">\\r\\n        <img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/proyectofinaljoomla\\/images\\/sesese.jpeg\\\" alt=\\\"Cr\\u00edticas a Bitcoin\\\">\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section-content\\\">\\r\\n        <h2>Cr\\u00edticas y Resistencia<\\/h2>\\r\\n        <p>\\r\\n            Desde su creaci\\u00f3n, Bitcoin ha sido objeto de cr\\u00edticas. Muchos lo consideran una burbuja especulativa o incluso una amenaza para la estabilidad financiera global. \\r\\n            Sin embargo, a pesar de las cr\\u00edticas, Bitcoin ha demostrado una notable capacidad para resistir la adversidad, manteni\\u00e9ndose firme en su misi\\u00f3n de descentralizar el control del dinero.\\r\\n        <\\/p>\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<!-- Section 3: El Futuro de Bitcoin -->\\r\\n<div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section-content\\\">\\r\\n        <h2>El Futuro de Bitcoin<\\/h2>\\r\\n        <p>\\r\\n            A pesar de los obst\\u00e1culos, Bitcoin sigue siendo una de las innovaciones m\\u00e1s disruptivas de la historia financiera. Su potencial para transformar \\r\\n            la econom\\u00eda global sigue siendo un tema de debate, lo que est\\u00e1 claro es que ha abierto un camino para otras criptomonedas y para una nueva forma de pensamiento econ\\u00f3mico.\\r\\n        <\\/p>\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n    <div class=\\\"section-image\\\">\\r\\n        <img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/proyectofinaljoomla\\/images\\/noooo.jpeg\\\" alt=\\\"El Futuro de Bitcoin\\\">\\r\\n    <\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<\\/body>\\r\\n<\\/html>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":9,\"created\":\"2025-01-01 20:45:33\",\"created_by\":\"209\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2025-01-05 14:22:29\",\"modified_by\":208,\"checked_out\":208,\"checked_out_time\":\"2025-01-05 14:20:39\",\"publish_up\":\"2025-01-01 20:45:33\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_s